Name: POST-EVA
checklistText:
Close the hatch using the [C] menu.
CABIN VENT - UP (CLOSED)
LT/RT SEC O2 BOTTLES - CLOSED
RAD - BYPASS
REPRESS knob - OPEN
Wait until the CABIN PRESSURE gauge reaches normal cabin conditions.
REPRESS knob - CLOSED
RAD - FLOW
RT SEC O2 BOTTLE - OPEN
CABIN AIR RECIRC - UP (OPEN)

POWER DOWN S/C
	RADAR - OFF
	PLATFORM - OFF
	RATE GYROS (3) - OFF
	EVENT TIMER - STOP
	AC POWER - OFF
	ACME BIAS PWR - OFF
	COOLANT PUMPS - AS DESIRED
	T/M - CMD
	MANEUVER THRUSTER C/B'S - CLOSED

Steps.Text: Close the hatch using the COMM/TOOLs menu.
Pay attention to the O2 level, and wait for cabin pressure > 5 PSIG.
Make a note of your CRYO Oxygen levels.
